2004-11-11  Christian Persch  <chpe@cvs.gnome.org>

	* src/ephy-main.c: (idle_unref), (main):

	Don't unref, then weak ref, then enter main loop; this won't work
	when refcount was 1. Instead weakref and unref on idle.
	Fixes bug #136170.

